platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Elemental magic rules the land of Teyvat in the remarkable Genshin Impactand as a powerful Traveler, you put this power to good use. Vibrant visual effects transform elemental blasts of fire, ice, and lightning into jaw-dropping spectacles. But its not just a looker: Genshin Impacts beautiful open world is filled with thrilling quests and fascinating secrets. Climb mountains, cook meals, and soar through the skies as you search for your lost siblingor simply get lost in Teyvat and see what happens.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Explore a new land, and meet amazing new characters.
